Package: AVOCADO
Type: Package
Title: Anomaly Vegetation Change Detection
Encoding: UTF-8
Version: 0.1.2
Date: 2024-10-28
Author: Mathieu Decuyper [cre, aut], Roberto O. Chávez [cre, aut], José A. Lastra [ctb]
Maintainer: <mathieu.decuyper@wur.nl>
Description: Anomaly based change detection algorithm that detects forest disturbance and regrowth in a continuous way. For more information, please check                the following paper: Decuyper et al. (2022) <https://doi.org/10.1016/j.rse.2021.112829>.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.6.0)
Imports: terra (>= 1.7-78), npphen, lubridate, stats
Suggests: sf, parallel
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/MDecuy/AVOCADO, https://www.pucv.cl/uuaa/labgrs/proyectos/tutorial-to-the-anomaly-vegetation-change-detection-avocado
BugReports: https://github.com/MDecuy/AVOCADO/issues
Roxygen: list(old_usage = TRUE)
Installation: install.packages("remotes")
              remotes::install_github("MDecuy/AVOCADO")
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
NeedsCompilation: no
